cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new pooling method for convolutional neural networks, which is a common technique used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method is inspired by attention methods (cs.AI) and involves joint training with the main network (cs.NE). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on benchmark problems involving image classification (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
